1
00:01:42,945 --> 00:01:45,105
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:02:21,545 --> 00:02:22,625
Here, let me help you.

3
00:04:07,225 --> 00:04:08,265
Okay.

4
00:04:08,345 --> 00:04:09,225
Sang…

5
00:04:18,145 --> 00:04:19,184
I guess

6
00:04:19,265 --> 00:04:20,665
I'll take this one with me.

7
00:04:20,745 --> 00:04:21,985
Okay.

8
00:04:22,064 --> 00:04:23,345
Perfect. One for each of us.

9
00:04:25,825 --> 00:04:27,225
Why don't we get something to eat?

10
00:04:30,865 --> 00:04:32,065
It's late.

11
00:04:32,145 --> 00:04:34,065
Why don't we go back to campus?

12
00:04:35,585 --> 00:04:37,065
Okay, let's go.

13
00:04:37,665 --> 00:04:38,585
Okay.

14
00:04:43,505 --> 00:04:44,665
I had fun today.

15
00:04:46,145 --> 00:04:47,065
Sang Zhi.

16
00:04:47,625 --> 00:04:49,505
Do you want to get dinner at the canteen?

17
00:04:50,705 --> 00:04:52,465
I'll just order takeout.

18
00:04:52,545 --> 00:04:53,425
You're back.

19
00:04:54,225 --> 00:04:55,585
-Hi.
-Come on.

20
00:04:56,305 --> 00:04:58,265
We were just talking
about spending New Year's Eve

21
00:04:58,345 --> 00:04:59,825
at the Central Plaza.

22
00:04:59,905 --> 00:05:02,305
Influencers recommend it.
We can get a lot of nice photos.

23
00:05:02,385 --> 00:05:03,225
Central Plaza?

24
00:05:03,305 --> 00:05:04,585
-Yes.
-It will be crowded.

25
00:05:04,665 --> 00:05:06,425
Right? That's what I told her.

26
00:05:06,505 --> 00:05:07,545
She wouldn't listen.

27
00:05:07,625 --> 00:05:08,505
Then…

28
00:05:12,905 --> 00:05:14,305
Why don't you join us, Jiang Ming?

29
00:05:14,385 --> 00:05:15,345
It's New Year's Eve.

30
00:05:15,425 --> 00:05:16,385
The more, the merrier.

31
00:05:16,465 --> 00:05:17,345
Right?

32
00:05:17,425 --> 00:05:18,265
Sure.

33
00:05:23,145 --> 00:05:24,665
I have to go back to my dorm.

34
00:05:24,745 --> 00:05:25,585
You guys carry on.

35
00:05:25,665 --> 00:05:26,505
Bye.

36
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:31,745
Did he win this for you

37
00:05:31,825 --> 00:05:32,825
from the claw machine?

38
00:05:33,385 --> 00:05:34,705
I got this myself.

39
00:05:34,785 --> 00:05:36,665
Well, what do you think about Jiang Ming?

40
00:05:39,505 --> 00:05:40,465
I think he's a good guy.

41
00:05:40,545 --> 00:05:41,665
He's handsome and nice.

42
00:05:41,745 --> 00:05:43,585
That brother of yours
can't be much better.

43
00:05:52,145 --> 00:05:54,185
Sangsang, I'll ask you one last time.

44
00:05:54,265 --> 00:05:55,825
Won't you spend New Year's Eve with us?

45
00:05:55,905 --> 00:05:57,385
I am sure.

46
00:05:57,465 --> 00:05:58,585
It's cold outside.

47
00:05:58,665 --> 00:06:00,065
But if you--

48
00:06:00,145 --> 00:06:01,705
No more buts.

49
00:06:01,785 --> 00:06:03,265
Sangsang already said no.

50
00:06:03,345 --> 00:06:05,305
Besides, the place will be crowded.

51
00:06:05,385 --> 00:06:07,545
We might see more heads than fireworks.

52
00:06:07,625 --> 00:06:08,905
That's right. Weiwei.

53
00:06:08,985 --> 00:06:10,345
You go ahead and enjoy yourself.

54
00:06:10,905 --> 00:06:12,305
-Let's go.
-All right.

55
00:06:30,705 --> 00:06:32,105
Wangwang.

56
00:06:35,025 --> 00:06:37,025
Are you trying to compete with me?

57
00:06:37,825 --> 00:06:39,625
This won't do. I have to change my outfit.

58
00:06:39,705 --> 00:06:41,985
No, Ning Wei. No need to change.

59
00:06:42,065 --> 00:06:43,945
You are the prettiest.

60
00:06:44,025 --> 00:06:45,865
You are the second prettiest.

61
00:06:45,945 --> 00:06:46,865
Okay. Great. Let's go.

62
00:06:46,945 --> 00:06:49,145
I think it's too short. I'll go change.

63
00:06:49,225 --> 00:06:50,305
It's not short. It's fine.

64
00:06:50,385 --> 00:06:52,425
It's perfect for this occasion. Let's go.

65
00:06:52,505 --> 00:06:54,385
-Let me get my coat.
-Okay.

66
00:06:54,465 --> 00:06:55,745
Hurry.

67
00:06:55,825 --> 00:06:56,905
-Sangsang.
-Let's go.

68
00:06:56,985 --> 00:06:58,425
Remember to eat.

69
00:06:58,505 --> 00:06:59,905
I know. I'll order takeout.

70
00:07:00,425 --> 00:07:01,745
We'll bring back tasty treats too.

71
00:07:02,305 --> 00:07:03,745
Don't miss us too much.

72
00:07:04,265 --> 00:07:05,105
Sangsang.

73
00:07:05,185 --> 00:07:06,665
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

74
00:07:07,465 --> 00:07:08,905
-We're off.
-Bye.

75
00:07:08,985 --> 00:07:10,705
-Bye.
-Bye. Remember to eat.

76
00:07:12,345 --> 00:07:13,345
Be careful.

77
00:07:13,425 --> 00:07:14,665
-Okay.
-There are a lot of people.

78
00:07:14,745 --> 00:07:15,945
Okay. Bye.

79
00:07:34,145 --> 00:07:34,985
There you are.

80
00:07:36,145 --> 00:07:37,705
I want to give Weiwei a surprise,

81
00:07:38,585 --> 00:07:40,465
but I don't want her to yell at me again.

82
00:07:41,225 --> 00:07:43,025
Why? Just tell her.

83
00:07:43,105 --> 00:07:44,385
Last time, I ordered hot pot

84
00:07:44,465 --> 00:07:45,905
and she yelled at me for three days.

85
00:07:46,385 --> 00:07:48,145
It's fine. There's always a next time.

86
00:07:49,065 --> 00:07:50,905
-Hello.
-Hi.

87
00:07:51,825 --> 00:07:52,985
Where's Weiwei?

88
00:07:53,065 --> 00:07:53,985
Hey!

89
00:07:57,225 --> 00:07:59,305
-Hi.
-Hi.

90
00:07:59,385 --> 00:08:01,065
You're not wearing glasses today.

91
00:08:02,465 --> 00:08:03,425
What do you think?

92
00:08:03,505 --> 00:08:05,385
Isn't she pretty without her glasses?

93
00:08:05,945 --> 00:08:07,145
Yes.

94
00:08:08,385 --> 00:08:10,465
Be more confident. Stand straight.

95
00:08:10,545 --> 00:08:12,025
Stop teasing me.

96
00:08:12,105 --> 00:08:14,305
Enough. It will be really crowded today.

97
00:08:14,385 --> 00:08:15,905
We won't get a spot if we don't go now.

98
00:08:15,985 --> 00:08:17,225
-Let's go.
-Where's Sang Zhi?

99
00:08:17,305 --> 00:08:18,505
Didn't she come with you guys?

100
00:08:18,585 --> 00:08:19,505
No.

101
00:08:19,585 --> 00:08:20,625
-She's not going.
-No.

102
00:08:21,185 --> 00:08:22,345
Is she not coming?

103
00:08:22,425 --> 00:08:24,025
Sangsang has never liked crowds.

104
00:08:24,105 --> 00:08:25,945
She'll stay in and watch anime. Right?

105
00:08:26,025 --> 00:08:27,305
-Yes.
-Yes.

106
00:08:27,385 --> 00:08:28,705
So let's go.

107
00:08:28,785 --> 00:08:30,425
-We're going to be late!
-That's right.

108
00:08:30,505 --> 00:08:31,345
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

109
00:08:31,425 --> 00:08:32,705
-Come on, Chen Qiang.
-Let's go.

110
00:08:32,784 --> 00:08:34,664
Come on. Jiang Ming, let's go!

111
00:08:36,465 --> 00:08:37,585
Okay, I'm the fifth wheel.

112
00:09:11,785 --> 00:09:12,705
Jiaxu.

113
00:09:12,785 --> 00:09:13,985
What are you doing?

114
00:09:15,585 --> 00:09:16,465
Nothing.

115
00:09:17,745 --> 00:09:19,745
There's a company dinner tonight.

116
00:09:19,825 --> 00:09:21,345
I can bring my family.

117
00:09:21,425 --> 00:09:22,665
I'll bring you.

118
00:09:22,745 --> 00:09:24,105
I'm not your family.

119
00:09:25,705 --> 00:09:27,065
I'll pass.

120
00:09:27,145 --> 00:09:28,865
I'm about to eat the takeout I ordered.

121
00:09:28,945 --> 00:09:30,465
Takeouts on New Year's Eve?

122
00:09:32,305 --> 00:09:33,905
If you don't like crowds,

123
00:09:34,385 --> 00:09:35,665
the two of us can have dinner.

124
00:09:39,945 --> 00:09:41,265
I don't feel like going out.

125
00:09:42,945 --> 00:09:44,465
You still owe me a meal.

126
00:09:44,545 --> 00:09:45,585
Are you trying to back out?

127
00:09:47,465 --> 00:09:49,385
I'll make a reservation right now.

128
00:09:49,465 --> 00:09:51,105
You get ready to come out.

129
00:09:51,945 --> 00:09:53,665
-I--
-I'm almost at your university.

130
00:09:58,345 --> 00:09:59,505
I'll get changed.

131
00:10:01,145 --> 00:10:02,825
Good. I'll call you when I get there.

132
00:10:14,425 --> 00:10:16,705
CHAPTER 11, MOVED

133
00:10:16,785 --> 00:10:18,625
IF THIS IS LOVE

134
00:10:31,385 --> 00:10:32,225
Try this.

135
00:10:36,625 --> 00:10:38,985
Why didn't you go out with your roommates?

136
00:10:39,065 --> 00:10:40,185
Do you guys not get along?

137
00:10:41,745 --> 00:10:42,665
No.

138
00:10:43,945 --> 00:10:45,865
We get along just fine.

139
00:10:45,945 --> 00:10:48,265
But they're going to the Central Plaza

140
00:10:48,345 --> 00:10:49,985
for the New Year's Eve countdown.

141
00:10:50,065 --> 00:10:51,065
It's too crowded for me.

142
00:10:52,065 --> 00:10:53,385
And Yihe is too cold.

143
00:10:53,465 --> 00:10:54,425
I didn't want to go out.

144
00:10:55,185 --> 00:10:56,785
But you said yes the minute I asked.

145
00:11:02,265 --> 00:11:03,425
That's because…

146
00:11:04,585 --> 00:11:06,945
That's because I owe you a meal.

147
00:11:07,025 --> 00:11:08,785
If I didn't come,

148
00:11:08,865 --> 00:11:10,265
you would think I'm trying

149
00:11:10,345 --> 00:11:11,905
to get out of treating you.

150
00:11:14,065 --> 00:11:16,025
I was just kidding about that.

151
00:11:22,465 --> 00:11:23,385
By the way,

152
00:11:24,585 --> 00:11:25,865
I didn't mean

153
00:11:25,945 --> 00:11:27,825
to tease you at the hospital.

154
00:11:34,025 --> 00:11:34,985
So

155
00:11:36,145 --> 00:11:39,305
I want to formally apologize to you today.

156
00:11:47,425 --> 00:11:48,865
You don't have to do that.

157
00:11:48,945 --> 00:11:50,705
It's not a big deal.

158
00:11:50,785 --> 00:11:52,585
Besides, that was a long time ago.

159
00:11:55,105 --> 00:11:56,105
All right.

160
00:11:57,225 --> 00:11:58,225
Eat more.

161
00:11:58,985 --> 00:12:00,145
It's my treat.

162
00:12:00,225 --> 00:12:01,345
Consider it my apology.

163
00:12:03,145 --> 00:12:04,705
Didn't we agree that it is my treat?

164
00:12:05,425 --> 00:12:07,185
I owe you a meal anyway.

165
00:12:07,745 --> 00:12:08,985
What do you mean?

166
00:12:09,705 --> 00:12:12,345
Are you saying
that we don't have to meet again

167
00:12:12,425 --> 00:12:13,905
after this meal?

168
00:12:18,385 --> 00:12:20,625
Have some sympathy
for this lonely old man.

169
00:12:21,185 --> 00:12:22,945
You won't even have a meal
with your brother.

170
00:12:26,945 --> 00:12:27,945
Jiaxu.

171
00:12:29,945 --> 00:12:31,105
Start digging in.

172
00:12:31,185 --> 00:12:32,905
You're really talkative today.

173
00:12:34,745 --> 00:12:37,265
It's not every day
that I get to have a meal with you.

174
00:12:37,345 --> 00:12:38,625
So what if I want to talk more?

175
00:12:40,545 --> 00:12:41,825
Let's talk about you.

176
00:12:43,105 --> 00:12:45,745
How are your classes?

177
00:12:46,505 --> 00:12:48,105
Are you interested in them?

178
00:12:50,665 --> 00:12:51,865
The professor says

179
00:12:52,385 --> 00:12:54,465
that freshmen don't have
many major courses.

180
00:12:55,265 --> 00:12:57,265
But we will have many as sophomores.

181
00:12:59,865 --> 00:13:01,065
Lame.

182
00:13:01,625 --> 00:13:02,465
Let's sit here.

183
00:13:02,545 --> 00:13:03,465
Okay, let's sit here.

184
00:13:10,745 --> 00:13:12,585
That's what my professor said.

185
00:13:17,425 --> 00:13:18,665
Why won't you answer my calls?

186
00:13:26,265 --> 00:13:27,585
I've told you.

187
00:13:28,305 --> 00:13:30,185
We don't need to stay in touch anymore.

188
00:13:32,745 --> 00:13:33,945
Jiang Ying!

189
00:13:38,745 --> 00:13:39,705
Who are you?

190
00:13:39,785 --> 00:13:41,025
What's wrong with you?

191
00:13:41,105 --> 00:13:42,305
And what's wrong with you?

192
00:13:42,385 --> 00:13:43,425
It's none of your business!

193
00:13:43,505 --> 00:13:44,745
Do you know why I did that?

194
00:13:44,825 --> 00:13:46,825
I don't care why.

195
00:13:46,905 --> 00:13:49,065
Listen, if you had assaulted him,

196
00:13:49,145 --> 00:13:50,465
I would've returned the favor.

197
00:13:52,065 --> 00:13:53,225
Jiang Ying!

198
00:13:58,825 --> 00:14:00,025
What do you want, Jiang Ying?

199
00:14:01,145 --> 00:14:02,985
Who is she, Duan Jiaxu?

200
00:14:03,465 --> 00:14:04,705
Jiang Ying, don't! Let's go.

201
00:14:04,785 --> 00:14:05,865
Sorry, miss. Please leave.

202
00:14:05,945 --> 00:14:07,105
Do you think you're in the clear?

203
00:14:07,185 --> 00:14:09,865
Listen, you owe me
for the rest of your life!

204
00:14:10,425 --> 00:14:11,905
-Please leave.
-Let's go.

205
00:14:11,985 --> 00:14:13,785
-You think you don't owe me anymore?
-Leave!

206
00:14:13,865 --> 00:14:14,905
-Duan Jiaxu!
-Get out!

207
00:14:14,985 --> 00:14:16,745
I will never let you off!

208
00:14:16,825 --> 00:14:18,105
Let me go!

209
00:14:19,145 --> 00:14:20,025
Jia…

210
00:14:21,385 --> 00:14:22,465
Are you okay?

211
00:14:24,305 --> 00:14:25,465
Let's leave, Jiaxu.

212
00:14:50,065 --> 00:14:51,865
It's cold. Put your coat on.

213
00:15:25,785 --> 00:15:26,865
So, Jiaxu.

214
00:15:27,665 --> 00:15:29,025
Who is that woman?

215
00:15:32,265 --> 00:15:33,265
Someone unimportant.

216
00:15:41,065 --> 00:15:42,145
To be precise,

217
00:15:43,785 --> 00:15:45,665
I guess she's my dad's former creditor.

218
00:15:48,385 --> 00:15:49,465
Wait!

219
00:15:49,985 --> 00:15:50,905
I'm going inside.

220
00:15:54,425 --> 00:15:55,825
I ran into her once.

221
00:15:56,545 --> 00:15:57,625
Did you?

222
00:15:58,545 --> 00:15:59,745
When you were hospitalized,

223
00:15:59,825 --> 00:16:01,385
I went to get your things at your place.

224
00:16:02,225 --> 00:16:03,705
We walked past each other.

225
00:16:04,265 --> 00:16:05,385
Did she do anything to you?

226
00:16:12,425 --> 00:16:13,705
So I guess

227
00:16:14,625 --> 00:16:16,025
she was there

228
00:16:17,305 --> 00:16:18,465
to see you.

229
00:16:20,265 --> 00:16:22,825
Does this happen every time she sees you?

230
00:16:25,505 --> 00:16:26,785
No.

231
00:16:39,865 --> 00:16:40,745
Jiaxu.

232
00:16:42,265 --> 00:16:43,545
As you said,

233
00:16:44,505 --> 00:16:46,145
she's your dad's former creditor.

234
00:16:47,225 --> 00:16:48,785
So it has nothing to do with you.

235
00:16:49,585 --> 00:16:51,305
You shouldn't let her bully you.

236
00:16:54,065 --> 00:16:54,985
I don't…

237
00:16:56,305 --> 00:16:57,985
There's no way she can bully me.

238
00:17:04,505 --> 00:17:05,345
What's the matter?

239
00:17:16,265 --> 00:17:17,265
I'm fine.

240
00:17:17,785 --> 00:17:18,825
I don't need…

241
00:17:37,665 --> 00:17:38,585
Does it hurt?

242
00:17:41,305 --> 00:17:42,185
No.

243
00:18:05,785 --> 00:18:06,985
I forgot to say this earlier.

244
00:18:12,105 --> 00:18:13,305
Thank you, Sang Zhi.

245
00:19:13,025 --> 00:19:14,745
I wish that all bad things

246
00:19:14,825 --> 00:19:16,745
will stay away from Jiaxu.

247
00:19:18,345 --> 00:19:19,985
I wish that someone could be with him.

248
00:19:20,785 --> 00:19:21,785
I wish

249
00:19:22,665 --> 00:19:23,785
that person is me.

250
00:19:33,705 --> 00:19:34,945
Aren't you going to make a wish?

251
00:19:35,425 --> 00:19:36,665
It's this year's first snowfall.

252
00:19:38,105 --> 00:19:39,465
Yihe doesn't get snow often.

253
00:19:40,385 --> 00:19:41,585
The last time it snowed

254
00:19:42,505 --> 00:19:44,025
was when I was in tenth grade.

255
00:19:46,385 --> 00:19:47,825
I guess

256
00:19:48,385 --> 00:19:49,545
I'm quite lucky.

257
00:19:50,785 --> 00:19:51,865
I'm lucky too.

258
00:19:52,905 --> 00:19:55,265
I get to see the snowfall with you.

259
00:20:02,985 --> 00:20:04,545
A wish at the first snowfall

260
00:20:04,625 --> 00:20:05,865
is said to come true.

261
00:20:16,985 --> 00:20:17,865
I wish

262
00:20:18,625 --> 00:20:21,705
Sang Zhi will always be happy and healthy,

263
00:20:22,585 --> 00:20:23,545
and so will I.

264
00:20:31,785 --> 00:20:33,225
What was your wish?

265
00:20:35,465 --> 00:20:37,025
It won't come true if I say it out loud.

266
00:20:38,465 --> 00:20:39,585
What did you wish for?

267
00:20:42,145 --> 00:20:43,985
It won't come true if I say it out loud.

268
00:21:14,225 --> 00:21:15,505
I wish…

269
00:21:18,385 --> 00:21:20,545
No, I can't let you guys hear it.

270
00:21:33,465 --> 00:21:34,825
What did you guys wish for?

271
00:21:35,705 --> 00:21:37,105
Of course,

272
00:21:37,625 --> 00:21:38,945
for us to be together forever.

273
00:21:41,745 --> 00:21:43,505
Goodness, I wish

274
00:21:43,585 --> 00:21:44,705
that I never have to listen

275
00:21:44,785 --> 00:21:46,105
to Ning Wei's mushy lines anymore.

276
00:21:46,185 --> 00:21:47,625
If you're so jealous,

277
00:21:48,985 --> 00:21:50,745
you should get a boyfriend too.

278
00:21:50,825 --> 00:21:51,665
That's right.

279
00:21:54,505 --> 00:21:55,545
Wangwang.

280
00:21:55,625 --> 00:21:56,785
