285
00:22:05,065 --> 00:22:07,065
This is the first snow in Yihe in years.

286
00:22:07,145 --> 00:22:08,665
But you don't have any wishes!

287
00:22:09,265 --> 00:22:10,625
You watch romance dramas, right?

288
00:22:11,305 --> 00:22:12,865
They always say

289
00:22:12,945 --> 00:22:14,265
