291
00:22:17,065 --> 00:22:17,945
Really?

292
00:22:18,025 --> 00:22:18,985
Of course.

293
00:22:19,065 --> 00:22:20,465
That's nonsense.

294
00:22:20,545 --> 00:22:22,585
The first snow calls
for beer and barbecue.

295
00:22:22,665 --> 00:22:23,905
Don't stand around. Come on.

296
00:22:24,505 --> 00:22:25,745
Good grief!

297
00:22:25,825 --> 00:22:27,425
She doesn't have a single romantic bone.

298
00:22:27,505 --> 00:22:29,385
You're single by your own virtue, Yu Xin.

299
00:22:29,465 --> 00:22:32,305
-Let's do it. Who will do it?
-Look, my boyfriend barbecues for me.

300
00:22:32,385 --> 00:22:33,505
Please!

301
00:22:33,585 --> 00:22:35,225
Let this year be over already.

302
00:22:43,545 --> 00:22:44,625
Jiang Ming.

303
00:22:46,425 --> 00:22:47,585
What did you wish for?

304
00:22:47,665 --> 00:22:48,785
Me?

305
00:22:51,625 --> 00:22:52,745
It's all right.

306
00:22:52,825 --> 00:22:54,345
You don't have to tell me

307
00:22:54,425 --> 00:22:55,345
if you don't want to.

308
00:22:55,945 --> 00:22:56,785
It's no big deal.

309
00:22:57,665 --> 00:22:59,465
I wished that the person I like

310
00:22:59,545 --> 00:23:00,665
would make a wish today

311
00:23:01,425 --> 00:23:03,225
and that her wish would come true.

312
00:23:08,345 --> 00:23:10,825
The person you like is really lucky.

313
00:23:13,545 --> 00:23:14,465
The meat is done!

314
00:23:14,545 --> 00:23:15,745
Do you guys want some or not?

315
00:23:16,305 --> 00:23:18,065
-Coming!
-Hurry!

316
00:23:18,145 --> 00:23:19,305
Let's head over.

317
00:23:42,385 --> 00:23:44,385
Jiaxu, I'm sorry.

318
00:23:44,465 --> 00:23:45,705
I was too impulsive today.

319
00:23:45,785 --> 00:23:47,265
Tell your friend that I apologize.

320
00:23:47,345 --> 00:23:48,225
I'm sorry.

321
00:23:49,985 --> 00:23:51,025
What's the point of this?

322
00:23:51,585 --> 00:23:53,465
Sorry, I won't do it again.

323
00:23:54,145 --> 00:23:55,225
Please move.

324
00:23:55,305 --> 00:23:57,265
I said I'm sorry, Duan Jiaxu!

325
00:23:57,345 --> 00:23:58,585
I already told you

326
00:23:59,065 --> 00:24:00,545
not to contact me anymore.

327
00:24:01,945 --> 00:24:04,025
So you're cutting me off
after paying off the debt?

328
00:24:04,105 --> 00:24:05,385
What gives?

329
00:24:05,465 --> 00:24:07,025
Don't you know that you owe me,

330
00:24:07,105 --> 00:24:08,345
Duan Jiaxu?

331
00:24:08,425 --> 00:24:09,825
What do I owe you? Tell me.

332
00:24:09,905 --> 00:24:11,385
Your dad killed my dad!

333
00:24:11,465 --> 00:24:12,385
You owe me!

334
00:24:12,465 --> 00:24:14,105
You know what you owe me!

335
00:24:17,985 --> 00:24:19,505
You just owe me.

336
00:24:21,025 --> 00:24:23,065
I've repaid what I should.

337
00:24:24,345 --> 00:24:26,385
My dad paid the price too.

338
00:24:27,665 --> 00:24:29,105
I don't owe you anything else.

339
00:24:29,865 --> 00:24:31,545
Duan Jiaxu!

340
00:24:34,225 --> 00:24:35,905
Duan Jiaxu!

341
00:24:35,985 --> 00:24:39,065
Don't forget what your mom promised us!

342
00:24:39,665 --> 00:24:42,705
She said you would always take care of me!

343
00:25:35,945 --> 00:25:37,825
Leave! You're not welcome here!

344
00:25:37,905 --> 00:25:38,745
Sorry, Mrs. Jiang!

345
00:25:38,825 --> 00:25:40,225
Get out. Leave.

346
00:25:40,305 --> 00:25:41,185
Leave now!

347
00:25:41,265 --> 00:25:42,825
-I'm sorry, Mrs. Jiang!
-Get out!

348
00:25:42,905 --> 00:25:44,265
-Mrs. Jiang.
-Why are you here?

349
00:25:44,345 --> 00:25:45,425
I'm sorry.

350
00:25:45,505 --> 00:25:47,585
He's dead! What's the use of these things?

351
00:25:47,665 --> 00:25:50,305
You destroyed my sister's family!

352
00:25:50,385 --> 00:25:51,585
Sorry.

353
00:25:51,665 --> 00:25:53,345
It's our fault.

354
00:25:53,425 --> 00:25:54,945
What is the use of saying sorry?

355
00:25:55,025 --> 00:25:57,665
Will that bring Xiaoying's dad back?

356
00:25:57,745 --> 00:26:00,145
What will Xiaoying and her mom do now?

357
00:26:03,585 --> 00:26:04,945
I want my dad.

358
00:26:07,585 --> 00:26:09,785
I just want my dad.

359
00:26:11,425 --> 00:26:12,345
Xiaoying.

360
00:26:13,065 --> 00:26:14,225
I'm sorry, Xiaoying!

361
00:26:14,305 --> 00:26:15,465
Mom!

362
00:26:15,545 --> 00:26:16,785
Mom, what are you doing?

363
00:26:16,865 --> 00:26:18,505
We've done you wrong.

364
00:26:21,225 --> 00:26:22,145
Rest assured.

365
00:26:23,185 --> 00:26:25,225
-Mom.
-We will take responsibility.

366
00:26:25,305 --> 00:26:27,625
We will pay the compensation
decided by the court.

367
00:26:27,705 --> 00:26:29,065
Even if we have to sell our house,

368
00:26:29,145 --> 00:26:29,985
take out a loan,

369
00:26:30,065 --> 00:26:31,225
or borrow money,

370
00:26:31,305 --> 00:26:32,665
no matter what,

371
00:26:33,225 --> 00:26:36,745
we will pay you on time.

372
00:26:37,465 --> 00:26:39,305
My son and I

373
00:26:40,265 --> 00:26:41,745
will look after you and your daughter

374
00:26:42,225 --> 00:26:44,225
for life as well.

375
00:26:44,865 --> 00:26:48,505
SORRY

376
00:27:27,425 --> 00:27:28,665
Jiang Ying.

377
00:27:29,265 --> 00:27:31,265
You've been away from school for a while.

378
00:27:31,825 --> 00:27:33,585
You can ask me if you need help.

379
00:27:39,905 --> 00:27:41,985
Did you know that Jiang Ying's dad died?

380
00:27:42,625 --> 00:27:43,585
I've heard.

381
00:27:44,305 --> 00:27:46,945
Apparently, Duan Jiaxu's dad ran him over.

382
00:27:47,025 --> 00:27:48,825
-Seriously?
-Yes.

383
00:27:48,905 --> 00:27:50,145
What are you guys talking about?

384
00:27:51,705 --> 00:27:52,785
Duan Jiaxu's dad ran over

385
00:27:52,865 --> 00:27:54,305
and killed Jiang Ying's dad.

386
00:27:54,385 --> 00:27:55,705
He was still alive at the time.

387
00:27:56,225 --> 00:27:57,825
He died after Jiaxu's dad fled the scene.

388
00:27:58,465 --> 00:28:00,705
Doesn't that make him a murderer's son?

389
00:28:00,785 --> 00:28:01,665
That's right.

390
00:28:10,385 --> 00:28:12,425
Doesn't that make him a murderer's son?

391
00:28:13,625 --> 00:28:15,385
How can he still come to school?

392
00:28:15,465 --> 00:28:16,465
If I were him,

393
00:28:16,545 --> 00:28:17,905
I wouldn't dare to show my face.

394
00:28:57,385 --> 00:28:58,505
I'm sorry, Mom.

395
00:29:02,545 --> 00:29:03,585
I can't do it.

396
00:29:18,905 --> 00:29:20,145
Jiaxu.

397
00:29:20,225 --> 00:29:21,825
As you said,

398
00:29:22,385 --> 00:29:24,265
she's your dad's former creditor.

399
00:29:25,385 --> 00:29:27,025
So it has nothing to do with you.

400
00:29:27,785 --> 00:29:29,305
You shouldn't let her bully you.

401
00:29:33,145 --> 00:29:33,985
Sang Zhi,

402
00:29:34,905 --> 00:29:35,905
thank you.

403
00:31:16,545 --> 00:31:19,625
SANG ZHI

404
00:31:19,705 --> 00:31:22,065
Happy New Year, Jiaxu.

405
00:31:22,145 --> 00:31:23,385
May you be happy every day.

406
00:31:26,345 --> 00:31:27,265
BROTHER NO. 2

407
00:31:27,345 --> 00:31:28,305
Happy New Year.

408
00:31:35,265 --> 00:31:36,465
I'm watching the fireworks.

409
00:31:37,265 --> 00:31:38,505
What about you?

410
00:31:45,665 --> 00:31:47,625
BROTHER NO. 2

411
00:31:47,705 --> 00:31:48,985
Me too.

412
00:31:49,705 --> 00:31:50,745
They're beautiful.

