00:32:13,825 --> 00:32:14,865
EDIT CONTACT DETAILS

414
00:32:14,945 --> 00:32:15,945
SANG ZHI

415
00:32:17,905 --> 00:32:21,225
ZHIZHI

416
00:32:21,305 --> 00:32:22,465
So, Jiaxu.

417
00:32:23,505 --> 00:32:24,825
Who is that woman?

418
00:32:26,345 --> 00:32:27,665
What do I owe you? Tell me.

419
00:32:27,745 --> 00:32:29,185
Your dad killed my dad!

420
00:32:29,265 --> 00:32:30,225
You owe me!

421
00:32:30,305 --> 00:32:32,185
You know what you owe me!

422
00:32:34,145 --> 00:32:36,345
Your voice sounds young,

423
00:32:36,425 --> 00:32:38,025
but you can't fool anyone.

424
00:32:38,105 --> 00:32:39,665
You're not young anymore.

425
00:32:39,745 --> 00:32:41,225
He is not my partner.

426
00:32:42,305 --> 00:32:43,745
He is too old.

427
00:32:43,825 --> 00:32:45,265
He is old enough to be my dad.

428
00:32:50,945 --> 00:32:52,745
SAVE CHANGES?

429
00:32:52,825 --> 00:32:53,705
SAVE

430
00:33:26,225 --> 00:33:27,825
DON'T SIT FOR TOO LONG

431
00:33:27,905 --> 00:33:29,465
GET UP AND MOVE, BYE

432
00:33:40,945 --> 00:33:41,865
DON'T SIT FOR TOO LONG,
GET UP AND MOVE, BYE

433
00:33:53,585 --> 00:33:54,945
Let me tell you guys something.

434
00:33:55,025 --> 00:33:56,625
I am getting married!

435
00:33:57,185 --> 00:33:59,185
I'm getting hitched!

436
00:33:59,265 --> 00:34:01,185
QIAN FEI

437
00:34:01,265 --> 00:34:02,545
I bet you're pissed!

438
00:34:03,985 --> 00:34:04,865
What's up?

439
00:34:04,945 --> 00:34:06,145
Are you all asleep?

440
00:34:06,665 --> 00:34:08,545
Why are you ignoring me
when I'm so excited?

441
00:34:09,905 --> 00:34:10,905
Not yet.

442
00:34:10,985 --> 00:34:17,585
DUAN JIAXU

443
00:34:20,264 --> 00:34:21,105
Well?

444
00:34:21,185 --> 00:34:22,065
You're still up?

445
00:34:22,145 --> 00:34:23,865
What? Did you miss me?

446
00:34:24,905 --> 00:34:25,784
I'm hanging up.

447
00:34:25,865 --> 00:34:27,105
Don't!

448
00:34:27,185 --> 00:34:29,025
If you're still up, chat with me.

449
00:34:29,105 --> 00:34:30,425
Guess what? I proposed today.

450
00:34:30,505 --> 00:34:31,625
Do you know how I proposed?

451
00:34:31,705 --> 00:34:33,264
When I saw her home today,

452
00:34:33,344 --> 00:34:34,744
I told her I was thirsty

453
00:34:34,824 --> 00:34:36,665
and to get me a bottle of water
from the trunk,

454
00:34:36,744 --> 00:34:37,985
so she did.

455
00:34:38,065 --> 00:34:39,185
The minute she opened it,

456
00:34:39,264 --> 00:34:40,425
she saw it filled with roses.

457
00:34:40,505 --> 00:34:42,065
I went up to her and said,

458
00:34:42,145 --> 00:34:43,665
"Will you be my wife?"

459
00:34:43,744 --> 00:34:44,784
Guess what she said?

460
00:34:44,865 --> 00:34:47,145
She said, "Won't that make me Mrs. Qian?"

461
00:34:47,225 --> 00:34:48,625
Isn't she cute?

462
00:34:49,744 --> 00:34:51,225
Nice.

463
00:34:52,465 --> 00:34:54,304
But I'm sad to hear

464
00:34:54,385 --> 00:34:55,784
that you're getting married.

465
00:34:56,465 --> 00:34:59,105
You always said
you were going to stay single with me.

466
00:34:59,185 --> 00:35:01,385
I only said that to make you feel better.

467
00:35:01,465 --> 00:35:02,545
Did you take it seriously?

468
00:35:05,425 --> 00:35:06,265
All right.

469
00:35:06,785 --> 00:35:08,265
Congratulations, buddy.

470
00:35:10,345 --> 00:35:12,505
Enough about me. What about you?

471
00:35:12,585 --> 00:35:15,425
Didn't you say
you were going on a blind date?

472
00:35:15,505 --> 00:35:16,665
Did you?

473
00:35:16,745 --> 00:35:18,785
What blind date? No way.

474
00:35:20,465 --> 00:35:21,985
Has anyone caught your eye?

475
00:35:22,065 --> 00:35:23,465
You must have feelings for someone.

476
00:35:36,105 --> 00:35:37,105
Jiaxu.

477
00:35:37,185 --> 00:35:39,025
I think I've caught a trace of something

478
00:35:39,105 --> 00:35:41,345
