479
00:35:41,425 --> 00:35:42,665
What's going on?

480
00:35:42,745 --> 00:35:44,185
Who is it?

481
00:35:44,265 --> 00:35:45,545
What do you…

482
00:35:45,625 --> 00:35:46,665
Tell me.

483
00:35:46,745 --> 00:35:47,985
Have you calmed down yet?

484
00:35:48,065 --> 00:35:49,065
Hurry up and go to sleep.

485
00:35:49,145 --> 00:35:50,465
You're about to be a married man.

486
00:35:50,545 --> 00:35:52,225
-No, tell me who it is.
-I'm hanging up.

487
00:36:02,985 --> 00:36:04,825
What am I thinking?

488
00:36:10,505 --> 00:36:15,785
NO MILK OR EGGS

489
00:36:17,305 --> 00:36:18,785
Kiddo.

