00:36:21,625 --> 00:36:24,785
CLEAR AMBITIONS, LEARNING,
SELF-CULTIVATION, AND DILIGENCE

491
00:36:25,705 --> 00:36:27,665
Weiwei, what did you buy?

492
00:36:27,745 --> 00:36:28,745
That's a huge box.

493
00:36:28,825 --> 00:36:29,905
Two pairs of shoes.

494
00:36:29,985 --> 00:36:31,185
They were on sale.

495
00:36:31,265 --> 00:36:32,505
I couldn't help it.

496
00:36:32,585 --> 00:36:34,105
-Jiaxu.
-What did you buy?

497
00:36:34,185 --> 00:36:35,745
-I have something for you.
-Stationery.

498
00:36:35,825 --> 00:36:36,745
Stationery?

499
00:36:36,825 --> 00:36:38,425
-I'll come to your office.
-How boring!

500
00:36:38,505 --> 00:36:39,745
Why buy stationery?

501
00:36:42,225 --> 00:36:43,665
-Weiwei.
-What did you buy, Sangsang?

502
00:36:43,745 --> 00:36:44,625
I bought…

503
00:36:45,665 --> 00:36:46,545
Chen Qiang.

504
00:36:46,625 --> 00:36:48,425
-Do you need help? I'll get that.
-I've got it.

505
00:36:48,505 --> 00:36:49,985
You have a class later. I'll manage.

506
00:36:50,065 --> 00:36:51,185
It's fine.

507
00:36:51,265 --> 00:36:52,505
Let's go eat after my class.

508
00:36:52,585 --> 00:36:53,665
Sure.

509
00:36:55,785 --> 00:36:56,825
Sang Zhi.

510
00:36:56,905 --> 00:36:58,785
You weren't there on New Year's Eve.

511
00:36:58,865 --> 00:37:00,385
Are you free this weekend?

512
00:37:00,465 --> 00:37:01,945
Let's decompress.

513
00:37:03,785 --> 00:37:05,065
But exams are around the corner.

514
00:37:05,145 --> 00:37:07,065
Maybe after we finish our exams.

515
00:37:07,145 --> 00:37:08,425
Exams?

516
00:37:09,225 --> 00:37:10,305
That's right.

517
00:37:10,385 --> 00:37:12,145
I have a friend who just opened up a bar.

518
00:37:12,225 --> 00:37:15,345
Why don't we all go there to celebrate
after our exams?

519
00:37:15,425 --> 00:37:17,665
Let's talk about that after our exams.

520
00:37:17,745 --> 00:37:18,945
What should we eat for dinner?

521
00:37:19,665 --> 00:37:20,745
That's right!

522
00:37:20,825 --> 00:37:22,585
I heard a new place opened up.

523
00:37:22,665 --> 00:37:23,505
Let's try it.

524
00:37:23,585 --> 00:37:24,545
I heard it's good.

525
00:37:24,625 --> 00:37:25,705
Tonight?

526
00:37:25,785 --> 00:37:27,625
You guys try it first.

527
00:37:27,705 --> 00:37:29,065
I'll pass tonight.

528
00:37:29,145 --> 00:37:30,345
Where are you going?

529
00:37:31,025 --> 00:37:33,665
I'm going to deliver a peephole camera

530
00:37:33,745 --> 00:37:34,585
to my relative.

531
00:37:35,905 --> 00:37:36,825
All right.

532
00:37:36,905 --> 00:37:38,385
I'll be leaving now.

533
00:37:38,465 --> 00:37:39,625
-Bye.
-Bye.

