00:38:53,025 --> 00:38:53,865
What's the matter?

560
00:38:53,945 --> 00:38:56,025
Jiang Ying is making a scene
again downstairs.

561
00:38:56,105 --> 00:38:57,745
I asked security to stop her.

562
00:38:57,825 --> 00:38:58,865
It should be fine.

563
00:39:26,705 --> 00:39:27,825
You cannot enter.

564
00:39:27,905 --> 00:39:29,225
Hold on. Wait at the entrance.

565
00:39:29,305 --> 00:39:31,185
-Listen! I'm looking for Duan Jiaxu!
-Wait.

566
00:39:31,265 --> 00:39:33,185
-He works here.
-I know what you're saying, miss.

567
00:39:33,265 --> 00:39:34,385
But you cannot enter yet.

568
00:39:34,465 --> 00:39:35,945
-I'm his friend.
-I'll help you.

569
00:39:36,025 --> 00:39:37,185
We'll let him know now.

570
00:39:37,265 --> 00:39:39,305
-If he gives permission--
-I just need to talk to him.

571
00:39:39,385 --> 00:39:41,145
Please wait here. Calm down.

572
00:39:41,225 --> 00:39:42,345
My colleague has--

573
00:39:42,425 --> 00:39:44,145
-Wait. You can't go inside.
-It's important!

574
00:39:44,225 --> 00:39:46,265
You can't enter. I know what you mean.

575
00:39:46,345 --> 00:39:48,025
-Please!
-Miss, you can't just enter.

576
00:39:48,105 --> 00:39:50,185
-Wait. You can't enter.
-I just need to say something.

577
00:39:50,265 --> 00:39:51,905
We're working. You cannot just go inside.

578
00:39:51,985 --> 00:39:52,945
-Please.
-Jiaxu.

579
00:39:53,025 --> 00:39:54,105
You cannot go inside.

580
00:39:54,745 --> 00:39:55,665
I'm his friend.

581
00:39:55,745 --> 00:39:57,345
My superior said we can't let you in.

582
00:39:57,425 --> 00:39:58,465
-Come.
-He must be upstairs.

583
00:39:58,545 --> 00:39:59,625
Mr. Duan isn't inside.

584
00:40:00,985 --> 00:40:02,425
Don't push me!

585
00:40:06,425 --> 00:40:07,585
Why didn't you pick up?

586
00:40:09,265 --> 00:40:11,145
Sorry, my phone ran out of battery.

587
00:40:11,225 --> 00:40:12,625
I forgot to charge it last night.

588
00:40:12,705 --> 00:40:14,145
Why didn't you tell me you were here?

589
00:40:15,345 --> 00:40:16,425
I did.

590
00:40:17,185 --> 00:40:19,065
I sent you a message. Didn't you see it?

591
00:40:19,145 --> 00:40:20,465
I was busy. I missed it.

592
00:40:21,185 --> 00:40:22,265
It's okay.

593
00:40:22,825 --> 00:40:23,665
Sang Zhi.

594
00:40:24,425 --> 00:40:27,065
Don't come straight to my office
or my place anymore.

595
00:40:27,145 --> 00:40:28,905
If you do, let me know beforehand, okay?

596
00:40:35,385 --> 00:40:36,705
Have you eaten?

597
00:40:44,945 --> 00:40:46,305
I wanted to give you this.

598
00:40:48,505 --> 00:40:49,625
A peephole camera.

599
00:40:50,425 --> 00:40:52,785
That woman keeps harassing you.

600
00:40:53,945 --> 00:40:56,025
You can install this on your door.

601
00:40:56,105 --> 00:40:57,425
It can connect to your phone.

602
00:40:57,505 --> 00:40:58,745
It's a smart camera.

603
00:40:58,825 --> 00:41:01,705
You can use it to call the police too.

604
00:41:01,785 --> 00:41:03,945
It will come in handy.

605
00:41:04,705 --> 00:41:06,265
That's all.

606
00:41:06,345 --> 00:41:07,505
Thank you.

607
00:41:08,105 --> 00:41:09,625
Go back to work.

608
00:41:09,705 --> 00:41:10,825
I'm going back to class.

609
00:42:55,865 --> 00:42:58,265
That woman keeps harassing you.

610
00:42:58,345 --> 00:42:59,185
SMART DOORBELL

611
00:42:59,265 --> 00:43:00,945
You can install this on your door.

612
00:43:01,785 --> 00:43:03,945
It will come in handy.
